2004-06-27 Flameeyes <dgp85@users.souceforge.net>
	Added bandwidth graph to Interface Statistics page.
	Now the SNMP-related tabs are shown only if SNMP is supported by the device. Similarly, logs are shown only if at least one CLI is supported.
	Errors in the driver file are now thrown as EInvalidDriver exceptions instead of set the driver itself invalid and then delete it.

